// Login History Endpoints

### Get All Login History
GET http://localhost:3000/api/login-history

### Get Login History by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/login-history/1

### Get Login History (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/login-history/99999

### Get Login History (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/login-history/invalid

### Get Player Login History
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/login-history

### Get Player Login History (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/login-history

### Create Login History
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login-history
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 1,
  "sessionId": "test-session-id"
}

### Create Login History (missing playerId)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login-history
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "test-session-id"
}

### Delete Login History
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/login-history/1

### Delete Login History (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/login-history/99999
